      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulation software (Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2) is under documented version control with traceability to release notes. SQA plan on file.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 is a commercially validated FEA solver with documented SQA processes. Version control logs and release validation reports were reviewed and found compliant with Gradation 2 requirements."
